import Link from 'next/link'
import CardComponent from '../components/sharedcomponents/Card'
import {Col,Row} from 'antd'
import styled from 'styled-components'

const Column = styled(Col)`
    text-align: center !important;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
`
const RowAnt = styled(Row)`
    text-align: center !important;
`

function HomePage() {

    return (
        <div>
            
           <RowAnt>
               <Column xl={4} lg={4} md={12} sm={12}>
                     <CardComponent
                        title = "Netflix"
                        price = "Rs. 350"
                        duration = "1 month"
                        imagesrc= "data:image/png;base64,"
                    />                   
           
               </Column>
               <Column xl={4} lg={4} md={12} sm={12}>
                     <CardComponent
                        title = "Netflix"
                        price = "Rs. 50"
                        duration = "1 month"
                        imagesrc= "data:image/png;base64,"
                    />                   
           
               </Column>
                <Column xl={4} lg={4} md={12} sm={12}>
                     <CardComponent
                        title = "Netflix"
                        price = "350"
                        duration = "1 month"
                        imagesrc= "data:image/png;base64,"
                    />                   
           
               </Column>
               <Column xl={4} lg={4} md={12} sm={12}>
                     <CardComponent
                        title = "Netflix"
                        price = "350"
                        duration = "1 month"
                        imagesrc= "data:image/png;base64,"
                    />                   
           
               </Column>
                <Column xl={4} lg={4} md={12} sm={12}>
                     <CardComponent
                        title = "Netflix"
                        price = "350"
                        duration = "1 month"
                        imagesrc= "data:image/png;base64,"
                    />                   
           
               </Column>
               <Column xl={4} lg={4} md={12} sm={12}>
                     <CardComponent
                        title = "Netflix"
                        price = "350"
                        duration = "1 month"
                        imagesrc= "data:image/png;base64,"
                    />                   
           
               </Column>
               
           </RowAnt>
           

        </div>
    )
}

export default HomePage
